      <h4 class="page-header" id="show">Retrieve an interlocutor</h4>
      <p>Retrieves the details of an existing interlocutor. You need only supply the unique interlocutor identifier that was returned upon interlocutor creation.</p>

      <pre>curl https://api.dialoganalytics.com/v1/interlocutors/:id?token=dialog-public-token</pre>

      <h4 class="page-header" id="index">List all interlocutors</h4>
      <p>Returns a list of the bot's interlocutors. The interlocutors are returned sorted by creation date, with the most recent interlocutors appearing first.</p>

      <pre>curl https://api.dialoganalytics.com/v1/interlocutors?token=dialog-public-token</pre>

